---
const personalImageAlt = "Lucas Martínez"
---

<div class="relative py-12">
  <!-- Background decorative elements -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0 -z-10">
    <div class="absolute top-1/3 right-1/4 w-64 h-64 bg-purple-500/5 rounded-full blur-3xl"></div>
    <div class="absolute bottom-1/4 left-1/3 w-48 h-48 bg-indigo-500/5 rounded-full blur-3xl"></div>
  </div>

  <div class="bg-white/5 dark:bg-gray-900/20 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-2xl p-8 border border-gray-200/20 dark:border-gray-800/30 shadow-xl">
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-5 gap-8">
      <!-- Image column with decorative elements -->
      <div class="md:col-span-2 flex justify-center items-center">
        <div class="relative group">
          <!-- Decorative elements -->
          <div class="absolute -inset-1 bg-gradient-to-tr from-purple-500/20 to-indigo-600/20 rounded-2xl blur-md opacity-70 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-500"></div>
          
          <!-- Main image -->
          <div class="relative">
            <div class="absolute -top-4 -left-4 w-8 h-8 bg-purple-500/30 rounded-full"></div>
            <div class="absolute -bottom-4 -right-4 w-12 h-12 bg-indigo-500/20 rounded-full"></div>
            
            <img 
              width="300" 
              height="300" 
              src="/yo.jfif" 
              alt={personalImageAlt} 
              class="relative z-10 object-cover w-full max-w-xs rounded-xl shadow-lg border-2 border-white/10 dark:border-gray-800/50 transform rotate-2 group-hover:rotate-0 transition-transform duration-300" 
            />
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Text column -->
      <div class="md:col-span-3">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800 dark:text-white mb-6 flex items-center">
          <span class="bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-600 to-indigo-500 bg-clip-text text-transparent lang-es">Sobre mí</span>
          <span class="bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-600 to-indigo-500 bg-clip-text text-transparent lang-en">About me</span>
          <div class="h-px flex-grow bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-600/50 to-transparent ml-4"></div>
        </h2>
        
        <div class="space-y-4 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 [&>p>strong]:text-purple-600 dark:[&>p>strong]:text-purple-400 [&>p>strong]:font-medium">
          <p class="relative lang-es">
            <span class="absolute -left-6 top-0 text-purple-500/30 text-4xl font-serif">"</span>
            ¡Hola! Soy <strong>Lucas Martínez Aguilera</strong>, estudiante de segundo año de Desarrollo de Aplicaciones Web (DAW) 💻. Desde que empecé en este mundo, me apasiona todo lo relacionado con el desarrollo web y disfruto enfrentándome a nuevos desafíos. Cada proyecto que realizo es una oportunidad para crecer y mejorar mis habilidades ⚙️.
          </p>
          
          <p class="relative lang-en">
            <span class="absolute -left-6 top-0 text-purple-500/30 text-4xl font-serif">"</span>
            Hello! I'm <strong>Lucas Martínez Aguilera</strong>, a second-year Web Application Development student 💻. Since I started in this field, I've been passionate about everything related to web development and I enjoy facing new challenges. Each project I undertake is an opportunity to grow and improve my skills ⚙️.
          </p>
          
          <p class="lang-es">
            Además, estoy comprometido con mantenerme al día en las <strong>tendencias tecnológicas</strong> 📊. Creo firmemente que la tecnología tiene el poder de transformar nuestro entorno, y estoy decidido a formar parte de ese cambio ⚡.
            <span class="absolute -right-2 bottom-0 text-purple-500/30 text-4xl font-serif">"</span>
          </p>
          
          <p class="lang-en">
            Additionally, I'm committed to staying up-to-date with <strong>technological trends</strong> 📊. I firmly believe that technology has the power to transform our environment, and I'm determined to be part of that change ⚡.
            <span class="absolute right-5 bottom-0 text-purple-500/30 text-4xl font-serif">"</span>
          </p>
          
          
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
